  "notes": "Pipeline 06: Enrich\n- Daily: find companies not enriched in last 7 days\n- SearXNG search for sanctions, ESG, certifications\n- Mistral 7B extracts structured risk data\n- Updates Neo4j node: risk_flags, certifications, sanctions_hit, risk_level"
